# ── AI test-classifier — derived skill directories ─────────────────────────
# .skills/ is the canonical, tool-neutral source of truth and IS committed.
# The directories below are per-developer derived copies produced by
# scripts/sync-skills.sh based on the developer's AI_REVIEW_TOOL setting.
# They are intentionally NOT committed so the repo isn't branded with any
# particular AI tool's directory name.
#
# NOTE: .github/copilot-instructions.md and .github/workflows/ai-test-classifier.yml
# ARE committed — they configure GitHub Copilot's PR review and the GitHub
# Actions workflow respectively, and are not derived from any other file. Only
# the .../skills/ subdirectory under each tool's location is gitignored.
.claude/skills/
.codex/skills/
.github/copilot/skills/

# ── Classifier output ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The workflow writes the per-run classification (P0 record / P1 audit trail)
# here before uploading it as a CI artifact. Not source-of-truth — don't commit.
classifier-out/
